{"tid":1357344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底講完何君堯未？一開連登熱門全撚部何君堯 肯關心上環36鎗班義士未呀？肯關心上環36鎗班義士未呀？","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T11:21:47.000Z","uid":89966,"like":62,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7b2f7820938980401e9e81afa48dfa7c9a08a8","tid":1357344,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:49:49.000Z","msg":"呢個係小弟cd-rom咁耐連登第一個post<br />\n真係實在睇到好撚柒嬲<br />\n我知元朗黑社會何妖單野係好爆<br />\n但唔洗成個熱門除左義士危殆，有可能死亡之外全撚部都何君堯呀？？？？<br />\n連登仔做乜撚野呀成班師奶咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大佬呀人地流血流淚幫你地頂36槍</span><br />\n而家何妖是但做一樣野就洗到你地版<br />\n我係何妖見到班連登仔咁易spin而家笑撚到合唔埋口啦<br />\n問心果句對唔對得住以後光復行動重返金鐘班勇武義士？<br />\n唔該你地每推1次何妖既post就推返3個有關上環義士單野出黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">班畜龍嬴晒啦鳩射幾十槍原來無人會理既</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">班義士連熱門都唔deserve咩？<br />\n唔該集中講返上環義士同黎緊元朗點為勇武派部處啦<br />\n係咪想今次比人斬36刀先值得大家討論呀<br />\n今日星期三啦啲裝備post路線post戰術post又去撚晒邊呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4014b6a6c9bf9b5a194510650d790cf6a9fcebe8","tid":1357344,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51ca66360f051dd978bf90e7eb09ee9ef8dd5879","tid":1357344,"uid":237077,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nBtCFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nBtCFX.jpg&h=a3d5aa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df351d160ef278c805806c5ea3b8ea7ba7ae0889","tid":1357344,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:50:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30dd8419423a93677dd66e5f79c3f03c0dd96274","tid":1357344,"uid":115264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n<sp